    <div class="about-section">
        <h1>About Me</h1>
        <img src="dayo-olatunbosun.jpg" alt="Dayo Olatunbosun">
        <p>Hello, I'm Dayo Olatunbosun, an emerging screenwriter passionate about storytelling. My journey into the world of screenwriting began with a deep love for films and an eagerness to create narratives that resonate with audiences. As an amateur, I am dedicated to honing my craft, exploring diverse genres, and bringing unique perspectives to the screen.</p>
        <p>With a background in literature and creative writing, I draw inspiration from a wide range of sources, from classic literature to contemporary cinema. I believe that every story has the power to inspire, provoke thought, and evoke a range of emotions.</p>
        <p>In my work, I strive to create characters that are authentic and relatable, and to craft plots that are engaging and thought-provoking. I am constantly learning and growing as a writer, and I am excited to share my journey with you.</p>
        <p>When I'm not writing, I enjoy watching movies, reading books, and exploring the vibrant culture and history of my hometown, Lagos, Nigeria. Thank you for visiting my website, and I look forward to connecting with you!</p>
